Was a bit slow to download, but turned out to be legit.

Still not sure how you got it up so fast, but thanks MP4SUX!

Sorry for those who didn't trust, but I understand it.

This is only the second time since I started that I got a jump on everybody.

How did I do it? Lots of hitting the "search" button until magically a WEB-DL shows.

That's UseNet, NZB & all that.

This is now two weeks in a row that the WEB-DL showed up first.

Don't know why, don't care. Sorry I'm just one guy with 2Mb/s U/L bandwidth.

It sure was fun watching the numbers climb above 6,000 and then the rollover ...

That's the magic tipping point when "peers" transfer to "seeds" and it's pretty.

And, as always, I wouldn't be able to do this without those sharing their
resources after the initial seed. Thank the thousand of you ...

AVIGUY

The place for the dis-gruntled to become re-gruntled ...

and the "yes it's real" comments after yours shows you to be somewhat
